  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `tg version 2021.05.1-alpha`\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nPending tx subscription should work\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nAttempting to create a new pending tx subscription crashes `rpcdaemon`\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\n```\r\nmkdir reproduction\r\ncd reproduction\r\nnpm install ethers\r\n```\r\n\r\ncreate an `index.js` file with the following content (assuming the rpcdaemon listens on 127.0.0.1:8545 with ws enabled)\r\n\r\n```\r\nconst ethers = require('ethers');\r\n\r\nconst provider = new ethers.providers.WebSocketProvider('ws://127.0.0.1:8545');\r\n\r\nprovider.on('pending', console.log);\r\n```\r\n\r\nand run `node index.js`\r\n\r\nshould make the `rpcdaemon` crash\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n````\r\npanic: assignment to entry in nil map\r\n\r\ngoroutine 198 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/filters.(*Filters).SubscribePendingTxs(0xc00015c7c0, 0xc000401ce0, 0x0, 0x0)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/filters/filters.go:97 +0xa5\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands.(*APIImpl).NewPendingTransactions.func1(0xc00015c840, 0xc0035702d0, 0xc00353f8f0)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands/eth_filters.go:82 +0xae\r\ncreated by github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands.(*APIImpl).NewPendingTransactions\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands/eth_filters.go:79 +0xae\r\nâžœ  ~ rpcdaemon --datadir /home/mortimr/data/tg --private.api.addr=localhost:9090 --ws --http.addr 172.17.0.1 --http.vhosts \"*\"\r\n````\r\n",
